about.summary: A sphinx extension which renders display math in HTML via JavaScript

name: sphinxcontrib-jsmath
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.0.1" %}

package:
  name: sphinxcontrib-jsmath
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/s/sphinxcontrib-jsmath/sphinxcontrib-jsmath-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: a9925e4a4587247ed2191a22df5f6970656cb8ca2bd6284309578f2153e0c4b8

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv"

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3.5
    - pip
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  requires:
    # This is a circular dependency b/c sphinx depends on this package now :-/
    - sphinx >=2
  imports:
    - sphinxcontrib
    - sphinxcontrib.jsmath

about:
  home: http://sphinx-doc.org/
  license: BSD-2-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: A sphinx extension which renders display math in HTML via JavaScript

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
